metadata.name: DoodlinTown #1
metadata.description: The DoodlinTown.Omg collection is comprised of 10,000 NFTs that will live in the Ethereum blockchain and were algorithmically created as well as hand-drawn by a group of Mexican artists. These bizarre characters represents a modern iteration of “chaneques”, Aztec mythological creatures associated with the netherworld, whose main task is to listen to and look after the hills and wild animals.
